            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
                <p>Ἀριστ[- -] on the underside of a foot - likely to be the beginning of a personal name - indicating
                    an ownership inscription. There would be too little space to include also a deity's name, making it a dedication. 
                    Sigma is four-bar, with very short lower bar; rho with a triangular loop, but there seems to have been 
                    an attempt to round it.</p>
            </div>
